abstract="Medical image analysis is one of the important and high critical applications of deep learning. In complex body organs like brain, it may be crucial to detect the brain tumor which may lead to some negative results. So, it is very important to safely detect the tumor in the brain which is not that easy to find out. In this research, the focus is on Deep Learning (DL) based Convolution Neural Networks (CNNs) approach as DCNN. For optimizing the weights, we applied Adam optimization technique. Having a huge dataset, it gives good accuracy which can be used for proper detection of tumor during the analysis and can go for diagnosis further. Different algorithms are implemented to test the proposed method, and their precision, recall performance parameters are estimated. This approach has given an accuracy of 98{\%} during the prediction.",
isbn="978-981-16-6887-6"
